content.acceptance_msg: READ THIS - This Time Attack Session is the qualifier session for the eNASCAR College iRacing Series powered by NACE Starleague.  While anyone can run the session, you must meet all eligibility requirements AND be registered to move on from this session.  Click 'READ RULES' for Registration, Rules and Eligibility.
Porsche Cars Canada, Ltd. is seeking the fastest 42 Canadian Sim Racers to race in an epic eight event series with a new team-based format.  Click the link to find the full rules and conditions.
